{"tid":645460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［東網］許智峯搶手機案件重演　郭偉強示範疑熊抱蔣麗芸","createTime":"2018-04-28T07:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T15:24:25.000Z","uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f62407574d9692b2035f57d0e95ed147a030ee6","tid":645460,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:04:15.000Z","msg":"民主黨立法會議員許智峯於立法會大樓內，搶走保安局女行政主任(EO)的手機，而全體立法會議員將可於明日(27日)的行政管理委員會特別會議上，觀看與事件相關的閉路電視片段，東網邀請到立法會議員蔣麗芸(Ann姐)及郭偉強，分別扮演女EO及許智峯，以模擬當日搶手機的事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生於立法會一地兩檢法案委員會期間，而會議室則位於立法會大樓的2樓，該樓層的升降機大堂有「狗仔隊」Ann姐駐守，並手持文件監察議員出入情況。而郭偉強突然走向Ann姐，查詢手上的文件為何，疑因Ann姐未有回答而一手搶走文件並撒到地上。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉強之後發現Ann姐手中緊握手機，便以手機作為目標，而Ann姐則被嚇至後退並將手機放到身後，防止手機被搶，但郭偉强未有放棄，更伸手繞到Ann姐身後企圖搶走手機，雖然Ann姐高舉手機以保護手機，但最終仍然難逃被搶命運。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉強搶走手機後，二人曾有所拉扯，而郭更向男洗手間逃走，但Ann姐一直着郭交還手機，並緊隨其後至洗手間門前。隨着郭偉強藏身男洗手間內，搶手機事件便告結束。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉強涉將蔣麗芸逼牆角 拉址環抱幾乎面對面<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180426/bkn-20180426194429232-0426_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180426%2Fbkn-20180426194429232-0426_00822_001.html&d=tbLlw32qYTf03B9dS5lvQ7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6907ae00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180426/bkn-20180426194429232-0426_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"de74dcee77b2c702398da411682bf7719e12c2ea","tid":645460,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"想借啲意抽水？人地蔣小姐大家閨秀"},{"pid":"022514908a2da00b1a9e380d9bfefad5ccf41321","tid":645460,"uid":63311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"等左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb04cc5d4b5e86b62ca2f00c0c4f77097e171e25","tid":645460,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"咀佢！咀佢！"},{"pid":"c7d8208e53c28c7cbd1c4fb820813665bb239cc9","tid":645460,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e3e856ddfc71277198751e0c9dd44886a27af64","tid":645460,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"313a7bf0e250b810615ccd6d0c57525a9dd8b4b9","tid":645460,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"a片提材"},{"pid":"a5c8243616be25ac7b284de8db72b765df9b0339","tid":645460,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"依家班保王黨想將件事集中喺搶手機到<br />\n<br />\n但佢被監視行蹤依件事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0106932bce18f78666cd44b5930d6230c64e1912","tid":645460,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de74dcee77b2c702398da411682bf7719e12c2ea","tid":645460,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"想借啲意抽水？人地蔣小姐大家閨秀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"佢個歌星妹三十年前幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}